data.description: Beautiful one-story home includes a gourmet kitchen with a large center island, gas cook top, built-in appliances and a walk-in pantry. The family room features two large windows and a door that opens onto the covered patio. Master suite includes a private bath with a garden tub, oversized mud set shower, double vanities and a walk-in closet. Private study perfect for a home office. Formal dining room. No neighbors behind home.
